      <h2>Buying Tea to Take Home</h2>
      <p>Most factory shops sell directly — you can buy fresh-picked and processed tea in attractive packaging at prices significantly lower than tourist shops in Colombo. Look for vacuum-sealed bags for freshness and choose whole-leaf grades rather than dust grades for the best experience at home. Mlesna and Dilmah are the most widely exported brands; at factory shops, look for estate-specific teas that are harder to find abroad.</p>
